OL,3,CMan admits murdering his elderly
OL,4,Cfather at home
OL,6,FA man has admitted murdering his
OL,7,Ffather at his home in Bath.
OL,9,FChristopher Monro, 30, pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto killing 73-year-old Peter Monro in
OL,11,FFebruary this year.
OL,13,FA carer found the elderly man with
OL,14,Fknife wounds in a bedroom at around
OL,15,Fnoon on 11 February.
OL,17,FEmergency services arrived at the
OL,18,Fscene but he was declared dead a short
OL,19,Ftime later.
