OL,6,FChristopher Monro had been due to
OL,7,Fstand trial at Bristol Crown Court on
OL,8,FMonday but changed his plea to guilty.
OL,10,FNo details of the case were outlined
OL,11,Fduring the brief hearing, but police
OL,12,Fhad previously said Mr Monro died from
OL,13,Fknife wounds.
OL,15,FMonro, of Osney Lane, Oxford, spoke
OL,16,Fonly to confirm his name and enter his
OL,17,Fplea.
OL,19,FJudge Julian Lambert remanded Monro
OL,20,Finto custody and adjourned the hearing
OL,21,Funtil sentencing on 7 November.
