OL,6,FDetectives discovered Monro had been
OL,7,Fstaying with his father the weekend
OL,8,Fbefore, with several people reporting
OL,9,Fhaving heard an argument two days
OL,10,Fpreviously.
OL,12,FDetectives traced Monro's movements
OL,13,Fand he was subsequently arrested at
OL,14,Fhis home address in Oxford.
OL,16,F'He refused to be anything other than
OL,17,Fhimself'
