OL,6,FIn a statement issued by police
OL,7,Ffollowing the guilty plea, Mr Monro's
OL,8,Ffamily said: "Peter Monro was an
OL,9,Fincredibly eccentric, funny,
OL,10,Fintelligent and unique man.
OL,12,F"He refused to be anything other than
OL,13,Fhimself. A man of his own time. No-one
OL,14,Felse's.
OL,16,F"His love of literature carried him
OL,17,Fthrough life, and his sharp mind was
OL,18,Fimpossible to beat."
