OL,6,FThey added: "This has been an
OL,7,Fextremely challenging time for Peter's
OL,8,Floved ones.
OL,10,F"We hope he is now with the swallows
OL,11,Fand thank Avon and Somerset Police for
OL,12,Ftheir professionalism and support
OL,13,Fthrough all of this.
OL,15,F"While life will never be the same
OL,16,Fagain for Peter's family, we can now
OL,17,Fmove forward with greater dignity and
OL,18,Fa deeper understanding of the need for
OL,19,Fcompassion and faith."
