OL,6,FDetective Inspector Neil Meade, who
OL,7,Fled the investigation, said: "The past
OL,8,Fsix months have been incredibly
OL,9,Fpainful time for Peter's family and
OL,10,Ftheir touching tribute to him is an
OL,11,Findication of how loved he was.
OL,13,F"This guilty plea comes following a
OL,14,Fcomprehensive police investigation and
OL,15,Fwe're grateful to Peter's family for
OL,16,Ftheir support while that process took
OL,17,Fplace, and the kind words they have
OL,18,Fsaid publicly.
