OL,6,F"We also wish to thank those people
OL,7,Fwho provided us with information in
OL,8,Fthe early hours of our investigation
OL,9,Fthat linked Christopher Monro to this
OL,10,Fcrime.
OL,12,F"That crucial detail enabled us to
OL,13,Fwork quickly and effectively with our
OL,14,Fcounterparts at Thames Valley Police
OL,15,Fto ensure Monro was apprehended at the
OL,16,Fearliest opportunity."
